<paragraph id="8BC6A742FF80FF9BF1F5FF1AECDAFE71" blockId="5.[174,1233,175,554]" pageId="5" pageNumber="392">
H o s t s. Species of 
<taxonomicName id="4C79DCC1FF80FF9BF0D2FF05EC0DFF32" authorityName="Del Guercio" authorityYear="1909" box="[452,573,175,201]" class="Insecta" family="Aphididae" genus="Eulachnus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="392" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
